{"tid":38573,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"開個 po 講下青前狗同容癌點樣開分身操控信眾","createTime":"2016-12-14T04:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T09:25:47.000Z","uid":37759,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9818262cc6146fa2e99df1724adca0aaf547f6e8","tid":38573,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:15:36.000Z","msg":"唔駛有行內人同例如包皮風呢d轉攪fb page同開分身嘅柒頭同我講<br />\n<br />\n淨係見睇今次堂主諗住借盤菜開拖，點之on99唔check清楚用左個仇教主陳雲嘅page去開火就知係點。<br />\n<br />\n次堂主諗住借盤菜開拖城邦派拖，點之on99唔check清楚用左個仇教主陳雲嘅page去開火。<br />\n<br />\n渠左唔緊要，成班青前狗同容癌洗版部隊即時上黎洗版spin走柒野，入唔到城邦入普羅，入唔到普羅就入熱狗。總之明明堂主柒左都洗到佢岩。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家一齊去奧樂蜜c飲品page比星就得，仲要記得課夠百六萬比青政比按金。<br />\n<br />\n冇成本又可以玩野，點解唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/cat9h4zt5/15439787_1618048125165002_4734088734390732262_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fcat9h4zt5%2F15439787_1618048125165002_4734088734390732262_n.jpg&h=272666e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706f674e44b593cda0b3726b48b64d800dc04dad","tid":38573,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2692a83e872851de1698369b229f92cff7e41ce6","tid":38573,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tVa13fV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtVa13fV.jpg&h=6af5efc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d30b9c1f7